=head1 DESCRIPTION

Suggestions for refining individual query terms. Suggestions are
returned as objects which note the term, suggested replacement, and its
index in the query.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> EndIndex => Int

End index of the parsed query.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> OriginalTerm => Str

The sub-string of the original query that is replaced by this query
term.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> RefinedTerm => Str

The term that will be suggested to the user.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> StartIndex => Int

Start index of the parsed component.



